OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,FIran has launched two missiles at
OL,7,FDiego Garcia, where there is a joint
OL,8,FUS-UK military base, after Washington
OL,9,Fwas given permission to use British
OL,10,Fbases for attacks in the Strait of
OL,11,FHormuz.
OL,13,FThe intermediate-range ballistic
OL,14,Fmissiles were fired at the facility `
OL,15,Fa key airfield for the US' heavy
OL,16,Fbomber fleet in the Indian Ocean, and
OL,17,Faround 2,370 miles from Iran's coast.
OL,19,FHowever, neither of the missiles
OL,20,Fstruck the base, an official told ITV
OL,21,FNews' North American partner CNN.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
