OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,FOne of the missiles was shot down by a
OL,7,FUS warship, while the other failed in
OL,8,Fflight, according to the Wall Street
OL,9,FJournal, citing multiple officials.
OL,11,FHaving previously limited the US to
OL,12,Fonly using the bases to hit missile
OL,13,Fsites targeting British interests in
OL,14,Fthe region, ministers in Downing
OL,15,FStreet agreed on Friday afternoon to
OL,16,Fwiden the scope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
