OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,FThe United States will now be allowed
OL,7,Fto use British bases to strike Iranian
OL,8,Fsites targeting the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,9,Fa crucial shipping channel through
OL,10,Fwhich around a fifth of the world
OL,11,Fpasses through.
OL,13,FDuring the course of the Middle East
OL,14,Fwar, Iran has choked off traffic
OL,15,Fthrough the passage, sending
OL,16,Fshockwaves through the global economy
OL,17,Fand threatening the supply of oil, gas
OL,18,Fand other commodities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
