OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump said the UK
OL,7,Fshould have acted a lot faster" in
OL,8,Fgiving the US permission, and called
OL,9,FNato allies "cowards" for refusing to
OL,10,Foffer warships to reopen the Strait.
OL,12,FTrump's rebuke of his transatlantic
OL,13,Fallies comes despite the president
OL,14,Fsaying the US was "getting very close
OL,15,Fto meeting (its) objectives" and that
OL,16,Fthe country is considering "winding
OL,17,Fdown" military efforts in the Middle
OL,18,FEast.
