OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,FSuggesting other countries would have
OL,7,Fto take the mantle, he wrote on his
OL,8,FTruth Social platform: "The Hormuz
OL,9,FStrait will have to be guarded and
OL,10,Fpoliced, as necessary, by other
OL,11,FNations who use it ` The United States
OL,12,Fdoes not!
OL,14,F"If asked, we will help these
OL,15,FCountries in their Hormuz efforts, but
OL,16,Fit shouldn't be necessary once Iran's
OL,17,Fthreat is eradicated."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
