OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,FHowever, defence sources have stressed
OL,7,Fthe situation was so dangerous that
OL,8,Fnot many nations would be willing to
OL,9,Fput warships "in the middle of that
OL,10,Fthreat right now".
OL,12,FIranian foreign minister Abbas
OL,13,FAraghchi said "Iran will exercise its
OL,14,Fright to self-defence" in response to
OL,15,Fthe UK's latest move.
OL,17,FPosting on X, he said: "Vast majority
OL,18,Fof the British People do not want any
OL,19,Fpart in the Israel-US war of choice on
OL,20,FIran.
