OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774231380
OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,F"Ignoring his own People, Mr Starmer
OL,7,Fis putting British lives in danger by
OL,8,Fallowing UK bases to be used for
OL,9,Faggression against Iran. Iran will
OL,10,Fexercise its right to self-defence."
OL,12,FThe UK government had previously
OL,13,Fgranted the US permission to use its
OL,14,Fbases for the "specific and limited
OL,15,Fdefensive purpose" of hitting missile
OL,16,Flaunch sites or storage depots in Iran.
OL,18,FWhen that decision was made, RAF
OL,19,FAkrotiri in Cyprus was hit by an
OL,20,FIranian drone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@dO]vD@OOUwD@RO]
