OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,7,Fdescribed Starmer's latest move as the
OL,8,F"mother of all U-turns" in a post on
OL,9,FX, while the Liberal Democrats and the
OL,10,FGreen Party said granting further
OL,11,Fpermission for the US to use British
OL,12,Fbases must first have a parliamentary
OL,13,Fvote.
OL,15,FThe prime minister will hold a Cobra
OL,16,Fmeeting next week to discuss plans to
OL,17,Fhelp households with the cost of
OL,18,Fliving caused by the war, it is
OL,19,Funderstood.
