OL,6,FIsrael strikes more targets in Tehran
OL,7,Fand Beirut
OL,9,FThe Israeli military said early
OL,10,FSaturday it was striking targets in
OL,11,FTehran.
OL,13,FThe announcement came shortly after
OL,14,Fthe military said it had begun a wave
OL,15,Fof strikes targeting Hezbollah
OL,16,Fpositions across the southern suburbs
OL,17,Fof Beirut, Lebanon.
