OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,FHours earlier, the army renewed
OL,7,Fevacuation warnings for seven
OL,8,Fneighbourhoods in Beirut's suburbs,
OL,9,Fprompting some residents to fire
OL,10,Fgunshots to alert families who had
OL,11,Freturned to flee.
OL,13,FNo casualties were immediately
OL,14,Freported.
OL,16,FGlobal tech supplies threatened as
OL,17,FQatar halts helium production
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
