OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,FIran's attack this week on Qatar's
OL,7,Fnatural gas export facility threatens
OL,8,Fto disrupt not just world energy
OL,9,Fmarkets but also global technology
OL,10,Fsupply chains because the helium it
OL,11,Fproduces is crucial for a range of
OL,12,Fadvanced industries.
OL,14,FBest known as the gas that makes party
OL,15,Fballoons float, helium is also a key
OL,16,Finput in chipmaking, space rockets and
OL,17,Fmedical imaging.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
