OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774231380
OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,FQatar supplies about 30% of the
OL,7,Fworld's helium, according to the US
OL,8,FGeological Survey, but the nation had
OL,9,Fto halt production shortly after the
OL,10,Fwar erupted three weeks ago.
OL,12,FThe latest Iranian strikes against the
OL,13,Fregion's energy producing
OL,14,Finfrastructure have added to supply
OL,15,Fworries, with Qatar's state-owned gas
OL,16,Fcompany saying it would crimp helium
OL,17,Fexports by 14%.
OL,19,FThere only are a handful of countries
OL,20,Fthat produce helium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
