PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774231380
OL,3,CMissiles fired at Diego Garcia after
OL,4,CUK lets US use bases for Hormuz strikes
OL,6,FThe United States is the biggest
OL,7,Fproducer, accounting for 81 million
OL,8,Fcubic meters last year. Qatar, Algeria
OL,9,Fand Russia are the other major
OL,10,Fproducers, but Russian supplies are
OL,11,Fbanned under US and European sanctions.
OL,13,FSouth Korea's semiconductor industry,
OL,14,Fwhich has seen a surge in global
OL,15,Fdemand for its chips amid the AI boom,
OL,16,Fis threatened by the Middle east war,
OL,17,Fwith the Seoul government monitoring
OL,18,Fdisruption of 14 semiconductor supply
OL,19,Fchain materials.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
